The capability monotonicity proof for Sail-CHERI-MIPS, comprising all
files except those in the directories "lib" and "sail-cheri-mips", are
subject to the licence below.  The "sail-cheri-mips" directory
contains a snapshot of the Isabelle theories generated from the
sail-cheri-mips specification and includes a copy of its licence.  The
"lib" directory contains snapshots of the Lem and Sail libraries and
includes copies of their licences.

